Why can't the uploader tell you what this series is about?  Duh...

Kid's show - appears on Nickelodeon.  The series stars Miranda Cosgrove as Carly, Jennette McCurdy as Sam, Nathan Kress as Freddie, and Jerry Trainor as Spencer. The series focuses on a girl named Carly who creates her own web show called iCarly with her best friends Sam and Freddie.
